## Attribution

This project includes implementations of:
- Optimal Transport algorithms (Sinkhorn, EMD)
- GPU-accelerated log-domain Sinkhorn solver
- Image color transfer using OT
- Distance metric benchmarking on machine learning tasks

Based on academic research in optimal transport theory and practical applications
in computer vision and machine learning.

## Disclaimer

This is an academic research project. The implementations are provided as-is for
educational and research purposes. For production use, consider using established
libraries like Python Optimal Transport (POT) or GeomLoss.
